name: InjectStreamStatus
description: States of importing an external video stream in the interactive live streaming.

parameters.StartSuccess: 0: The external video stream is imported successfully.

parameters.StartAlreadyExists: 1: The external video stream already exists.

parameters.StartUnauthorized: 2: The external video stream to be imported is unauthorized.

parameters.StartTimedout: 3: A timeout occurs when importing the external video stream.

parameters.StartFailed: 4: The SDK fails to import the external video stream.

parameters.StopSuccess: 5: The SDK successfully stops importing the external video stream.

parameters.StopNotFound: 6: The external video stream to be stopped importing is not found.

parameters.StopUnauthorized: 7: The external video stream to be stopped importing is unauthorized.

parameters.StopTimedout: 8: A timeout occurs when stopping importing the external video stream.

parameters.StopFailed: 9: The SDK fails to stop importing the external video stream.

parameters.Broken: 10: The external video stream is corrupted.
